{"tid":1973450,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"67歲婦涉親吻不同政見青年被控非禮　求以其他方式解決","createTime":"2020-04-15T08:02:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-15T09:18:54.000Z","uid":229185,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ef2ba57d646a44e5c7f0ea1536a92ddcfb104a22","tid":1973450,"uid":229185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T08:02:21.000Z","msg":"六旬婦因政見分歧而被圍堵公園，期間疑因無計可施而突然親吻一名青年，兼襲擊對方。老婦因而被控一項非禮罪及兩項普通襲擊罪。案件今（15日）在西九龍裁判法院再訊，辯方申請押後案件以便給予被告法律意見，以及與控方商討可否以其他方式處理本案，裁判官終准案件押後至5月27日。<br />\n<br />\n手足比人非禮<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32dd0c3bea4c1cc279fb32b3c2efc906fb2d700c","tid":1973450,"uid":229185,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T08:07:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13e6ef48c4d50d99bab134b180571151e114560c","tid":1973450,"uid":40272,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T08:36:27.000Z","msg":"屌 有咩搵我 攪著啲細路做咩姐"},{"pid":"3bc29b02ee70f7a0c912fec8932a53b310fd2f4b","tid":1973450,"uid":275238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T08:41:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/lzkSyya3EKs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FlzkSyya3EKs&d=kRIfmd%2Br1GQrfPRU1wEKQPQJlsOaju8aQhUrU01WOmc%3D&h=eeeffbda\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/lzkSyya3EKs</a>"},{"pid":"db37fd895f40176d9f45a05bdeedf9e8c1a63982","tid":1973450,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T08:41:55.000Z","msg":"想私底下性交贖罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gi